OL,3,C'I'm 100% committed to the team' -
OL,4,CSwindon Town owner calls for unity
OL,6,FSwindon Town's owner has said that he
OL,7,Fis still 100% committed to the
OL,8,Ffootball club despite some fans urging
OL,9,Fhim to sell up.
OL,11,FThe club's supporters posted an open
OL,12,Fletter to Clem Morfuni last month
OL,13,Fsaying they had 'lost confidence' in
OL,14,Fthe direction of the team.
OL,16,FIt came after a disastrous league
OL,17,Fcampaign, one of the worst in the
OL,18,Fclub's recent history, where the
OL,19,FRobins avoided relegation out of the
OL,20,Ffootball league.
