OL,6,FNow the owner has spoken to ITV for
OL,7,Fthe first time about how the public
OL,8,Fletter affected him but also his plans
OL,9,Ffor the future.
OL,11,F"It was tough, it has been a tough
OL,12,Ftime for everyone connected with this
OL,13,Ffootball club," he said.
OL,15,F"I totally get it but I feel like we
OL,16,Fare putting things in place now to try
OL,17,Fand move forward.
