OL,3,C'I'm 100% committed to the team' -
OL,4,CSwindon Town owner calls for unity
OL,6,F"The letter is not nice and I totally
OL,7,Funderstand it but I have thick skin
OL,8,Fand I am not the sort of person who
OL,9,Fcan turn around and walk away.
OL,11,F"I am 100% committed to this team, I
OL,12,Fwouldn't be doing everything I am
OL,13,Fdoing if I wasn't.
OL,15,F"Football is religion to these fans
OL,16,Fhere and I understand that and I will
OL,17,Fbe trying to improve communication
OL,18,Fwith them.
