OL,3,C'I'm 100% committed to the team' -
OL,4,CSwindon Town owner calls for unity
OL,6,F"I get their frustration, I have put
OL,7,Fmillions in to this club. I am not
OL,8,Fhappy either so we are working to move
OL,9,Fforward with it.
OL,11,F"If someone comes along and says that
OL,12,Fthey are interested in buying this
OL,13,Fclub and the vision they have and the
OL,14,Fprospect they offer is good I am happy
OL,15,Fto look at it."
OL,17,FMr Morfuni bought the club, in what
OL,18,Fwas a hostile takeover, in the summer
OL,19,Fof 2021.
