OL,6,FThe team narrowly missed on promotion
OL,7,Fto League One that season, losing to
OL,8,FPort Vale on penalties in the play-
OL,9,Foffs.
OL,11,FThe following season was a more
OL,12,Fdifficult one for the team and
OL,13,Ffinancial struggles off the pitch
OL,14,Fstarted to emerge.
OL,16,FLast year Mr Morfuni was also charged
OL,17,Fby the EFL for transferring some of
OL,18,Fhis ownership shares without proper
OL,19,Fapproval.
