OL,6,FSince then he has had to officially
OL,7,Fdeny rumours that the club is up for
OL,8,Fsale on numerous occasions and claims
OL,9,Fto have put more than #8 million of
OL,10,Fhis own money in to the team since he
OL,11,Ftook over.
OL,13,FMoving forward the team is now managed
OL,14,Fby Mark Kennedy, who was previously in
OL,15,Fcharge of Lincoln City.
OL,17,FHe will hope to secure its future in
OL,18,Fthe football league next year, with Mr
OL,19,FMorfuni saying that he has been given
OL,20,Fa significant budget for the coming
OL,21,Fcampaign.
